# 🔁 Day 3: DevOps Workflow

## 💡 DevOps Loop
∞ Plan → Code → Build → Test → Deploy → Monitor → Feedback

---

## ⚙️ Workflow Breakdown

### 1. Plan
Define goals, create tasks, and manage requirements using tools like Jira

### 2. Code
Develop using Git for version control

### 3. Build
Compile & package application (Maven)

### 4. Test
Run automated tests (Selenium)

### 5. Deploy
Release to production using CI/CD tools (Jenkins)

### 6. Monitor
Track performance and logs

### 7. Feedback
Continuously improve based on monitoring insights

---

